graph TD
    %% 0. Ingestion Surfaces
    subgraph Ingestion ["0. Multi-Surface Ingestion"]
        API["REST API"]
        CLI["CLI / dcode"]
        MCP["MCP Server"]
        WS["WebSocket/SSE"]
        SDK["Python SDK"]
    end

    Ingestion -->|Trigger execution| User([User Prompt / File Path])
    
    %% 1 & 2. Firewall and CEO
    User -->|API / CLI / MCP| Interceptor[1. Epistemic Interceptor / Firewall]
    WORM[("WORM Database Quarantine")] -.->|Cryptographically Persist| Interceptor
    
    Interceptor -->|Cryptographic Proxy| CEO[2. Factory CEO Orchestrator]
    
    %% 3. Librarian / Interrogate Loops
    CEO -->|Needs Codebase Summary| Librarian[Librarian PM]
    Librarian -->|Deconstruct & Extract| ContextComp[Context Compressor Agent]
    ContextComp -->|Compressed context| CEO
    
    CEO -->|Missing Details| Interrogate[User Interrogation / Multiple Choice]
    Interrogate -.->|Ask Clarification| Ingestion
    
    %% 4. Saturation and PM Delegation
    CEO -->|Context Saturated| PMs{PM Routing}
    PMs -->|Agent Specs| AgentPM[3a. Agent PM]
    PMs -->|Backend| BackendPM[3b. Backend PM]
    PMs -->|Frontend| FrontendPM[3c. Frontend PM]
    
    %% 5. Maker-Checker Loop
    subgraph Maker-Checker Loop
        %% Agent PM Workflow
        AgentPM -->|Run Maker| PromptEng[Prompt Engineer Agent]
        PromptEng --> YAMLComp[YAML Compiler Agent]
        YAMLComp -->|Compiled YAML| Validator[Agent Validator Checker]
        
        %% Backend PM Workflow
        BackendPM -->|Run Maker| FastAPICoder[FastAPI Coder Agent]
        FastAPICoder -->|Compiled Backend Code| Validator
        
        %% Frontend PM Workflow
        FrontendPM -->|Run Maker| UIDesigner[UI Designer Agent]
        UIDesigner --> ReactCoder[React Coder Agent]
        ReactCoder -->|React Component Code| Validator
        
        %% Validation Decision
        Validator -->|Check Standards| ValidDecide{Is Valid?}
        ValidDecide -->|No - Feedback| Remediation{Attempts < 3?}
        Remediation -->|Yes| PromptEng
        Remediation -->|Yes| FastAPICoder
        Remediation -->|Yes| UIDesigner
        Remediation -->|No - Fail| ExecutionFail[Execution Failure]
        ValidDecide -->|Yes| Export[4. Platform Exporter]
    end
    
    %% 6. Egress & DB Checkpoints
    Export -->|ZIP Archive| Out([Installable Agent Package])
    Checkpointer[("Postgres Checkpointer")] -.->|Persist State Checkpoint| Export
